# AVD-AWS-0104 — Unrestricted egress on Lambda security group
# Lambda functions require outbound internet access to reach AWS APIs and third-party endpoints.
AVD-AWS-0104

# AVD-AWS-0057 — IAM policy uses wildcard resource
# Resource ARNs are not known at plan time (dynamic bucket/table names).
# Scope will be tightened post-deployment using actual ARNs.
AVD-AWS-0057

# AVD-AWS-0011 — CloudFront WAF not enabled
